ied (no AI).","test_description":"Instantiate the real persistent queue with a fixed capacity, enqueue up to limit, then enqueue one more and assert rejection plus unchanged persisted size.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.1,"Integration":0.74,"System":0.14,"Agentic":0.01,"Workflow":0.01}}]}
